Package: msuopa
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for the MSU OPA Team
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ian C", "Johnson", email = "ian.johnson@montana.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ian C Johnson <ian.johnson2@montana.edu>
Description: A variety of functions serving as wrappers to allow for easier
    data extraction, transformation, and loading. Primarily focused on HR 
    related datasets. Requires the installation of Rtools on the machine
    compiling the package. See https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/Rtools/
